name: babygenderrevealgirl
0:
”Alexa, tell baby gender”
”Alexa, open baby gender”
”Alexa, ask baby gender to reveal gender”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: baby gender
des: This skill can be used at baby reveal party. This skill is to reveal Baby Girl. For Baby Boy, you can add "baby gender reveal boy". But don't add both the skills at the same time, as both use the same skill invocation name. Install either "baby gender reveal girl" or "baby gender reveal boy".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
